OL,5, A US national held in Saudi Arabia has 
OL,6, received a 16-year jail sentence for   
OL,7, writing tweets critical of the         
OL,8, government, his son has told the BBC.  
OL,10,FSaad Ibrahim Almadi, 72, who also has  
OL,11,FSaudi citizenship, was arrested in     
OL,12,FNovember after he travelled from       
OL,13,FFlorida to Riyadh to see his family.   
OL,15,FHis son has now spoken out for the     
OL,16,Ffirst time publicly, going against what
OL,17,Fhe says has been US official advice.   
OL,19,FIbrahim Almadi said he did not want to 
OL,20,Fsee his father die in prison.          
